      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about being \"terrified\" anymore. it's more like i'm just tired of the noise of trying to exist when nothing changes. if i just... stopped existing, it wouldn't be a tragedy. it would just be like a tab closing on a browser. quiet, simple, and nobody would have to deal with the mess of a person who isn't really there anyway. dont you think there's a certain kind of peace in just fading away?",
